@startuml
title UC15 - Frontend Classes
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
class ForgotPasswordPage { email +submit(): void }
class ResetPasswordForm { token newPassword confirm +validate(): ValidationResult +submit(): void }
class ValidationMessage { message +render(): JSX }
class AuthApiClient {
  +forgotPassword(email): Promise<void>
  +resetPassword(token, newPassword): Promise<void>
}
ForgotPasswordPage --> AuthApiClient
ResetPasswordForm --> ValidationMessage
ResetPasswordForm --> AuthApiClient
note bottom of ResetPasswordForm
  Validate password policy (>=8, chữ + số) trước khi submit.
  token lấy từ query string của link email.
end note
@enduml
